# Example Package - Usage Guide

## Basic Usage

### CMake Integration

Add to your `CMakeLists.txt`:

```cmake
find_package(example-package CONFIG REQUIRED)
target_link_libraries(your_target PRIVATE example-package::example-package)
```

### Features

Enable optional features:

```cmake
# Feature 1 (depends on some-other-package)
vcpkg install example-package[feature1]:x64-windows

# Feature 2
vcpkg install example-package[feature2]:x64-windows

# Multiple features
vcpkg install example-package[feature1,feature2]:x64-windows
```

## Example C++ Code

```cpp
#include <example-package/example.hpp>

int main() {
    example::HelloWorld();
    return 0;
}
```

## Building Your Project

With vcpkg toolchain:

```bash
cmake -B build -S . \
    -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=/d/code_tools/c_plus_plus_tools/vcpkg/vcpkg/scripts/buildsystems/vcpkg.cmake
cmake --build build
```